name: Where's Mommy?
description: SometimesNFTS.io - From our New Series: "Danse Macabre". This piece is a real physical creation. It includes an antique doll head from the 1950's-1960's, part of a set of twins, with original eyes. Ethically sourced cow vertebrae. Red latex for blood tears. The doll head used on this piece was removed and used on another piece by the same artist called: "The Charred". This physical piece, in its entirety no longer exists. SometimesNFTS.io Exclusive Artist: Jason Jost - NFT created by: Z3ROH3RO
